      "content": "Please, do not take St. John's Wort with Sertraline; it is a dangerous combination that can cause serotonin syndrome, a serious medical emergency. You need to speak with your prescribing physician immediately about your low mood before finals. They can safely adjust your current dosage or suggest a different, appropriate supplement.",
