      "content": "i get that, but my doctor is literally impossible to reach before the semester ends and i'm already starting to spiral. if i can't talk to them, isn't there some kind of way to balance it out? like, if i space them out by a few hours or maybe take a certain amount of something else to offset the risk? i just need something helpful since i can't wait weeks for an appointment.",
